  "markdown": "FREE SHIPPING ON ORDERS $50+\n\n## YOUR BAG![YOUR BAG](https://feastables.com/cdn/shop/files/your-bag-text.svg?v=1705023389&width=1)\n\n(0ITEMS)\n\n\nYOU\n\n- START\n\n$0\n\n\nYOU\n\n- START\n\n$0\n\n\n- Free Shipping\n\n$75\n\n\n\\|\nFREE\n\nADD\n\n\\|\nFREE\n\nADD\n\n- \\|\nFREE\n\n\n\n\n\n\n   -\n\n+\n\n\nDELETE\n\n\n### YOUR BAG IS EMPTY\n\n[BROWSE ALL PRODUCTS](https://feastables.com/pages/our-cocoa-story)\n\n### YOUR BAG IS EMPTY\n\n[BROWSE ALL PRODUCTS](https://feastables.com/collections/all)\n\nSUBTOTAL\n\n$0.00$0.00\n\n[VIEW BAG & CHECKOUT](https://feastables.com/checkout)\n\n\\*TAXES & ALL THAT JAZZ ARE CALCULATED AT CHECKOUT\\*\n\n\n#### TRY ONE OF OUR FAVORITES!\n\n[![View Mario Galaxy Cocoa Crunch](https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0551/6060/2784/files/Chocolate_MarioGalaxyCocoaCrunch_60g_400x400.png?v=1776111170)](https://feastables.com/products/mario-galaxy-cocoa-crunch-chocolate?variant=63169743257969&_rdiscovery-handle=mario-galaxy-cocoa-crunch-chocolate&_rdiscovery-widget=221083)\n\n##### [Mario Galaxy Cocoa Crunch](https://feastables.com/products/mario-galaxy-cocoa-crunch-chocolate?variant=63169743257969&_rdiscovery-handle=mario-galaxy-cocoa-crunch-chocolate&_rdiscovery-widget=221083)\n\nPrice$29.99\n\nADD\n\n[Powered by Rebuy](https://rebuyengine.com/?shop=feastables.myshopify.com)\n\n![OUR  COCOA STORY](https://feastables.com/cdn/shop/files/aboutus-hero-mobile_ff2afbf0-1884-4636-a98c-11a5dd394017.jpg?v=1752094509&width=480)\n\n![](https://feastables.com/cdn/shop/files/aboutus-storycards-bg-web.png?v=1752096299&width=2560)![](https://feastables.com/cdn/shop/files/aboutus-storycards-bg-mobile.jpg?v=1752095288&width=2048)\n\n- ## FEASTABLES   BEGAN AS A FUN,  BETTER-FOR-YOU   SNACK BRAND\n\n\n\n\ninspired by MrBeast's journey with Crohn's and his mission to make great-tasting, accessible snacks.\n\n\n- ![old sea salt bar](https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0551/6060/2784/files/abouts-slides-1-oldbar.png?v=1752181128&width=500)\n\n\n\n![old crunch bar](https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0551/6060/2784/files/abouts-slides-1-oldbar2.png?v=1752181301&width=450)\n\n\n\n![old almond bar](https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0551/6060/2784/files/abouts-slides-1-oldbar3.png?v=1752251333)\n\n\n\n![abstract shape](https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0551/6060/2784/files/aboutus-slides-1-shape1.png?v=1751397606&width=140)\n\n\n\n![abstract shape](https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0551/6060/2784/files/aboutus-slides-1-shape3.png?v=1751397606&width=150)\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\nOUR FIRST LAUNCH\n\n\n\n\n## THE MRBEAST BAR, WASN'T   JUST A   CHOCOLATE BAR\n\n\n\n\nIt was a flavor-packed adventure, complete with gamified experiences, fan engagement,and over-the-top stunts.\n\n\n- AS WE GREW, SO DID\n\n\n\n\n## OUR STANDARDS &   OUR RESPONSIBILITY\n\n\n\n\nfor what we make and what we stand for. We reformulated our recipes for an even bigger, bolder flavor and redesigned our packaging and bars to match.\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n![New Mr.Beast Milk Chocolate Bar](https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0551/6060/2784/files/aboutus-slides-3-newbar.png?v=1751400309&width=600)\n\n\n\n![Chocolate Chunk](https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0551/6060/2784/files/aboutus-slides-3-chunk2.png?v=1751404862&width=212)\n\n\n\n![Chocolate Chunk behind milk chocolate bar](https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0551/6060/2784/files/aboutus-slides-3-chunk2.png?v=1751404862&width=212)\n\n\n\n![New Mr.Beast Cookies and Creme Bar](https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0551/6060/2784/files/aboutus-slides-3-newbar2.png?v=1751401356&width=600)\n\n\n\n![Exploded Peanut Butter Bar](https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0551/6060/2784/files/aboutus-slides-3-newbar3.png?v=1751401497&width=600)\n\n\n\n![Chocolate Chunk](https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0551/6060/2784/files/aboutus-slides-3-chunk1.png?v=1751404861&width=212)\n\n\n\n![Chocolate Peanut Butter Chunks](https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0551/6060/2784/files/abouts-slides-3-pbexp.png?v=1752176891&width=350)\n\n\n\n![Chocolate Peanut Butter Chunks 2](https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0551/6060/2784/files/abouts-slides-3-pbexp2.png?v=1752177280&width=160)\n\n- ![Cocopod Left](https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0551/6060/2784/files/aboutus-slides-4-cocopod.png?v=1751405520&width=550)\n\n\n\n![Cocopod Right](https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0551/6060/2784/files/aboutus-slides-4-cocopod2.png?v=1751405547&width=550)\n\n\n\n\n\n\nALONG THE WAY WE UNCOVERED\n\n\n\n\n## THE HARD TRUTH   BEHIND    THE COCOA INDUSTRY\n\n\n\n\nand how cocoa is farmed in some regions. 1.5 million kids in child labor, widespread poverty, and systemic injustice.\n\n\n- WE KNEW WE HAD\n\n\n\n\n\n\nTO TAKE A STAND\n\n\n\n\n\nAnd change chocolate for good\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\nWE KNEW WE HAD\n\n\n\n\n\nTO TAKE A STAND\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\nAND CHANGE\n\n\n\n\n\nCHOCOLATE FOR GOOD\n\n\n\n![](https://feastables.com/cdn/shop/files/Ethical-Sourcing-About-Us-texture.png?v=1748378095&width=700)\n\n![](https://feastables.com/cdn/shop/files/aboutus-mission-topleftimage.png?crop=center&height=352&v=1750967183&width=320)\n\n![](https://feastables.com/cdn/shop/files/aboutus-mission-toprightimage.png?crop=center&height=128&v=1750968148&width=135)\n\n![](https://feastables.com/cdn/shop/files/aboutus-mission-bottomleftimage.png?crop=center&height=200&v=1750968496&width=320)\n\n![](https://feastables.com/cdn/shop/files/aboutus-mission-bottomrightimage.png?crop=center&height=420&v=1750967227&width=380)\n\n![TONY'S OPEN CHAIN ](https://feastables.com/cdn/shop/files/Tony-Sticker.png?crop=center&height=100&v=1748971908&width=124)\n\n## Now, At The Core Of  Feastables is   A New Mission\n\nEradicate child labor in the cocoa industry. Our cocoa is 100% Fairtrade certified. We pay farmers the living income reference price or the market price, whatever is higher! And we only partner with farms that actively protect children. And there’s more to come.\n\nWe Still Bring The Fun  \\- Now With\n\nNow With\nBolder\n\n\nFlavor And\n\nA Bigger Purpose\n\nFrom chocolate bars to cups and beyond, every bite helps build a better future for the people behind it.\n\n[LEARN MORE ABOUT OUR MISSION](https://feastables.com/pages/ethicalsourcing)\n\n![](https://feastables.com/cdn/shop/files/aboutus-learnmore-cup.png?v=1751050464&width=1000)\n\n![](https://feastables.com/cdn/shop/files/aboutus-learnmore-bar.png?v=1751050464&width=1000)\n\nJOIN THE CREW!\n\n\nfeastables.com\n\n# feastables.com is blocked\n\nThis page has been blocked by an extension\n\n- Try disabling your extensions.\n\nERR\\_BLOCKED\\_BY\\_CLIENT\n\nReload\n\n\nThis page has been blocked by an extension\n\n![](<Base64-Image-Removed>)![](<Base64-Image-Removed>)\n\nfeastables.com\n\n# feastables.com is blocked\n\nThis page has been blocked by an extension\n\n- Try disabling your extensions.\n\nERR\\_BLOCKED\\_BY\\_CLIENT\n\nReload\n\n\nThis page has been blocked by an extension\n\n![](<Base64-Image-Removed>)![](<Base64-Image-Removed>)\n\nshop.app\n\n# shop.app is blocked\n\nThis page has been blocked by an extension\n\n- Try disabling your extensions.\n\nERR\\_BLOCKED\\_BY\\_CLIENT\n\nReload\n\n\nThis page has been blocked by an extension\n\n![](<Base64-Image-Removed>)![](<Base64-Image-Removed>)",
